data.description: Are you looking for a place to call your own? Discover a delightful two-story residence just moments away from schools, restaurants, & shopping. This home is a balance of convenience & modern living! Be greeted by an appealing great room displaying soft carpeting & tile flooring, a soothing palette, & sliding glass doors to ensure the space is bathed in natural light. The kitchen boasts granite counters, subway tile backsplash, recessed lighting, cabinets w/crown molding, a pantry, matching appliances, & an island w/breakfast bar. A versatile loft area is perfect for a reading nook! The main bedroom offers a private bathroom w/dual sinks & walk-in closet. Low-care courtyard has a covered patio, ready to host gatherings & weekend BBQs. See it now!
